    "texte_orig": "No...![1205][001E][SP]That[SP]wasn't[SP]it,[SP]Jun...[1205][001E][SP]What[SP]we[SP]just\nsaw[SP]wasn't[SP]what[SP]happened[SP]at[SP]all!",
