  {
    "id": 9,
    "offset": 282492,
    "slot_size": 244,
    "data_size": 240,
    "nom_orig": "Maya",
    "texte_orig": "What[SP]in[SP]the[SP]world[SP]is[SP]that?[1205][001E][SP]I[SP]bet[SP]it's[SP]what's\nmaking[SP]rumors[SP]into[SP]reality...[1205][001E][SP]And[SP]controlling\nJun-kun[SP]too...",
