    "nom_orig": "Eikichi",
    "texte_orig": "The[SP]memories[SP]from[SP]that[SP]summer[SP]are[SP]important\nto[SP]me...[1205][001E][SP]For[SP]Ginko[SP]and[SP]Big[SP]Maya,[SP]too.[SP]For[SP]all\nof[SP]us,[SP]really...",
